data.description: This absolutely charming home is bursting with possibilities and waiting for you to make it yours! With 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 2 spacious living areas, there's ample room for relaxation, entertainment, and creating unforgettable memories.  Step through the front door and be greeted by the inviting main living area, boasting high vaulted ceilings and a cozy fireplace. To the right, discover the serene bedrooms, including a generously-sized Owner's Suite featuring a walk-in closet and a private bathroom for added comfort and convenience.  The kitchen is a modern marvel, with butcher block style countertops and crisp white cabinetry creating an atmosphere of both functionality and elegance. Adjacent to the kitchen, a delightful breakfast area invites you to start your day right, while a tucked-away formal dining room sets the scene for more intimate gatherings.  But the excitement doesn't stop there! Venture into the expansive second living area, complete with its own private entry, offering endless possibilities as a movie room, home gym, or your dream home office – the choice is yours!  Step outside into your own private oasis, where the amenities abound. A screened porch area beckons for lazy afternoons, while a covered patio provides the perfect spot for al fresco dining. Need a space for hobbies or DIY projects? Look no further than the wired workshop with a convenient roll-up door. And for the little ones (or the young at heart), a playset and above-ground pool promise endless hours of fun in the sun.  Plus, enjoy the benefits of COUNTY ONLY TAXES, adding even more value to this incredible property. Conveniently located near I-75, shopping, and dining, and zoned for Houston County High School, this home truly has it all.  Don't let this opportunity pass you by – this home is as cute as a button and packed with endless potential! Schedule your private showing today and prepare to fall in love with everything it has to offer. Call now before it's too late!
